Class StreamDocumentBuilder

    DocumentBuilder<StreamDocumentBuilder,Document>

    public class StreamDocumentBuilder
extends AbstractDocumentBuilder<StreamDocumentBuilder,Document>
implements DocumentBuilder<StreamDocumentBuilder,Document>
    The StreamDocumentBuilder is used to build StreamDocuments. StreamDocuments are used for XML extraction and so on. To create a StreamDocumentBuilder use AcrolinxFactory.documents().
